      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ANTHEIA (5) was outgraded in the G3 Vamos Stakes a month ago but brought compelling form to that. Yet to miss the frame in three starts over this course and distance, and has a low gate and some weight relief. Much better placed and rates the one to beat. GEEGEEHAILSTORM (6) has been nudged out at her last three starts and deserves a change of luck. Draws awkwardly but keeps the top hoop and is well placed. Can hit the line hard. NOVALARGO (2) races forward and boosted her figures this track/trip, winning a CL1. Jumped a $3 favourite in a 60 against the above following, but didn't finish it off. Peaks now, and is worth another chance. ESPRIT DIVA (7) did about what was expected at Hobart first-up over this trip and is proven second-up. Backs up quickly, and she can run into it.",
